data.description: This beautiful three-bedroom, 1 bathroom move in ready home offers updated electric, newer, furnace, newer, hot water tank, vinyl, siding, and all new laminate flooring throughout. The large living room and dining room will give you plenty of space to entertain, as well as the updated kitchen. Just off the kitchen there is a three-season sunporch to enjoy. Upstairs you will find a large primary bedroom with walk-in closet as well as two additional large bedrooms. Also, upstairs you will find the updated full bathroom with a tub, shower, combo and a pedestal sink. You will also enjoy the semi wooded lot with off-street parking for up to three cars. Don’t miss this opportunity to call this house HOME!
